ygData.msgSnippet: Stay broke? Yeah I do that, I had 50 plat twice, and blew it on jewel craft. then I saved up 25 for when I turned level 12, and blew that 4 on spells. so yeah,
ygData.messageBody:
Stay broke? Yeah I do that, I had 50 plat twice, and blew it on jewel craft.
then I saved up 25 for when I turned level 12, and blew that 4 on spells. so
yeah, I'd say I stay broke, more by spending sprees than lack of income.
Fiera Mindbender [BAD]
Erudite Enchanter-Xegony
